<plot>Production number 5302 in Universal-International "Name Band Musical" series of shorts featuring Lionel Hampton and His Orchestra, with a much-larger-than usual number of supporting acts. Featured are band vocalists 'Sonny Parker (II)' (qv) and 'Lorene Carter.' (qv); 'Curley Harner' (qv) doing a comedy dance and 'Kitty Murray' (qv) in a comedy skit; 'Lawrence Williams (V)' (qv) and dance- team partner 'Lillian Williams (I)' (qv), and disc jockey 'Joe Adams (IV)' (qv) introduces the numbers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?337337</url></doc>
